{"tid":331770,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"mbp retina 2015甩鍍膜，求解決方法","createTime":"2017-07-22T12:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T11:09:08.000Z","uid":54611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94bc4659e6eb3ead8c1e9373d2465b67a7059379","tid":331770,"uid":54611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:34:25.000Z","msg":"pro<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gkfldu19\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgkfldu19&h=3947e189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上年9月中買左macbook pro 2015(有買applecare)，慢慢開始個mon出現左d keyboard印，我用LCD清潔水+眼鏡布都抹唔走，最近呢個月更加嚴重，mon中間大面積出現點點同橫線印。想問下大家咁係咪鍍膜甩左，有冇咩方法清走or去天才吧整？洗唔洗錢去換moon？自問都好惜mbp"},{"pid":"fc132ffefdb7acc7bf4892f934feaafec2ffdb82","tid":331770,"uid":62326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"有保養拎去換唔洗錢"},{"pid":"b320658f03ae562ce5b4ca3f3ca788e01fedcbc7","tid":331770,"uid":15793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:42:16.000Z","msg":"有無保養都可以換"},{"pid":"29a1ff6180b7b0c2071e0b7d900294ae17332ee5","tid":331770,"uid":54611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:47:34.000Z","msg":"Apple會唔會話係我人為損壞，要我加錢？"},{"pid":"41591df50d48728abd02a108d60c53ec05f4f673","tid":331770,"uid":15793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:07:41.000Z","msg":"鍍膜問題，就算個moon經人為損壞都換得，本身製造時質素問題"},{"pid":"f86c6b8d35bed1cfb8fc98b0e8cb8bf8ea5382bd","tid":331770,"uid":15793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:10:30.000Z","msg":"According to Apple article OP1564:<br />\n&quot;C. Eligibility - Displays with a confirmed anti-reflective display coating issue are eligible for display replacement at no charge - including displays with accidental damage.&quot;"},{"pid":"9a78e0f37256b4064ca833ebbfb374938d0b38b6","tid":331770,"uid":102607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:14:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"htt